Noah Fleiss https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noah_Fleiss 0 Noah Fleiss (born April 16, 1984) is an American film and television actor. He was born in White Plains, New York. He is known for his role as Chris in the video game Until Dawn. Fleiss's great uncle is Professor Joseph L. Fleiss, and he is a distant relative of Dr. Paul Fleiss, Mike Fleiss, and Heidi Fleiss.
